name: r-sigtree

owner.description: Bioconda is a distribution of bioinformatics software realized as a channel for the versatile Conda package manager.
owner.name: bioconda

summary: Provides tools to identify and visualize branches in a phylogenetic tree that are significantly responsive to some intervention, taking as primary inputs a phylogenetic tree (of class phylo) and a data frame (or matrix) of corresponding tip (OTU) labels and p-values.
